articles.title: Officers
articles.summary: This document lists the current officers of an organization, detailing their specific roles and providing their names along with corresponding phone numbers. The listed positions include President, Vice President, Treasurer, and Secretary/Bulletin Editor.

articles.title: Board Members
articles.summary: This document provides a straightforward list of individuals designated as "Board Members". It simply presents the names of the people who currently serve on the organization's board.

articles.title: Bulletin for August and September, 1973
articles.summary: This bulletin covers events and activities for the San Jose Amateur Astronomers (SJAA) for August and September 1973. It recaps the annual banquet and mentions upcoming general meetings featuring talks on telescope nomenclature and an eclipse expedition, as well as an equipment night. The bulletin also lists scheduled star parties, board meetings, a regional conference, and details about public viewing opportunities at Lick Observatory, while also including a reminder about membership renewals.
